.annotationLayer .textWidgetAnnotation input.comb:focus {
  /*
   * Letter spacing is placed on the right side of each character. Hence, the
   * letter spacing of the last character may be placed outside the visible
   * area, causing horizontal scrolling. We avoid this by extending the width
   * when the element has focus and revert this when it loses focus.
   */
  width: 115%;
}

              景元
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Jing Yuan</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/69e521ac5be0e70740c60f89ec2200ba_92954136854239853.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">孙晔</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">位列帝弓七天将之一的「神策将军」，外表懒散、心思缜密。<br><br>不以危局中力挽狂澜为智策，因此在常事上十分下功夫，以免节外生枝。<br><br>因其细心谋划，仙舟承平日久，看似行事慵懒的景元反被送上绰号「闭目将军」。</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; z-index: -1000; pointer-events: none;"><object type="text/html" tabindex="-1" data="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/saved_resource.html" style="display: block;               彦卿
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Yan Qing</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/efe0cd9e61117776212f07f0a783bbb7_5028448997740896061.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">喵酱</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll hasVBar" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden scroll; margin-right: -15px;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">意气飞扬的云骑骁卫，仙舟「罗浮」最强剑士。<br><br>为剑生亦为剑痴，当彦卿手中握剑时，无人敢小看这位尚在总角之年的天才。<br><br>或许能让手中宝剑微微收敛锋芒的，只有时间。</p></div><div style="display: block;               白露
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Bai Lu</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/69e521ac5be0e70740c60f89ec2200ba_9141386202820537658.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">多多</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">性格活泼的小女孩，持明族的「衔药龙女」，药到病除的名医。<br><br>经常开出不拘一格的药方，如「多喝热水」、「睡一觉就好了」。<br><br>见不得人受苦，治病时总是闭着眼睛。<br><br>——总之病好了就行！</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; z-index: -1000; pointer-events: none;"><object type="text/html" tabindex="-1" data="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/saved_resource(2).html" style="display: block;               停云
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Ting Yun</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/69e521ac5be0e70740c60f89ec2200ba_3547373252073710941.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">蒋丽</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">八面玲珑的狐人少女，天舶司商团「鸣火」的首席代表。<br><br>停云天生生得一副慧心妙舌，但凡她开口，人们就免不了想听她多说几句。在她的调度下，仙舟的贸易庆典逐渐声名远扬。<br><br>能不战斗就尽量不去战斗，能劝为己用就尽量劝为己用——这便是停云的原则。</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; z-index: -1000; pointer-events: none;"><object type="text/html" tabindex="-1" data="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/saved_resource(3).html" style="display: block; z-index: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(1, 169, 154, 0); border: none; width: 6px; top: 0px; bottom: 6px; right: 0px;"></div><div class="__rail-is-horizontal" style="position: absolute; z-index: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(1, 169, 154, 0); border: none; height: 6px; left: 0px; right: 6px; bottom: 0px;"></div></div></div></div><div data-v-b64f4e70="" data-swiper-parallax="-60%" data-swiper-parallax-duration="600" class="left"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="char-name">
              素裳
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Su Shang</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/f6a04b7a0e5ae87e8c1e55ed71c6a6a5_2014147579892578121.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">陈婷婷</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll hasVBar" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden scroll; margin-right: -15px;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">单纯热心的云骑军新人，执一柄重剑。<br><br>憧憬着云骑军历史上的传奇，渴望成为响当当的人物。<br><br>为此，素裳坚决恪守「急人所急，有求必应；日行一善，三省吾身」的信条，过着助人为乐的忙碌日子。</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; z-index: -1000; pointer-events: none;"><object type="text/html" tabindex="-1" data="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/saved_resource(4).html" style="display: block;               青雀
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Qing Que</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/e2191f60c2db324785c9cd95b9b4fcb9_7956470892650781155.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">刘十四</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">太卜司的普通卜者，在「忙里偷闲」这件事上绝不偷闲。<br><br>顺应父母的期望考入太卜司，却发现本以为清闲的铁饭碗是高强度的职场苦海。<br><br>经过数年历练，青雀终于磨砺了一身本领——无论部门流转，她仍旧是最低职级的卜者。<br><br>没事翻翻书，玩玩古代牌戏…人生如此，夫复何求？</p></div><div style="display: block; class="left"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="char-name">
              卡芙卡
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Kafka</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/69e521ac5be0e70740c60f89ec2200ba_826515654311681066.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">徐慧</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%;               银狼
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Silver Wolf</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/e2191f60c2db324785c9cd95b9b4fcb9_829728630093130597.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">Hanser</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll hasVBar" style="height: 100%;               姬子
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Himeko</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/59e1513a7415c4145d990218c174851a_3087845843355005860.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">林簌</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">充满冒险精神的科学家，少女时代在故乡遭遇了搁浅的星穹列车。<br><br>若干年后，当姬子终于修复列车驶入群星时，她意识到这只是个开始。在「开拓」新世界的道路上，需要更多的同伴——<br><br>即使同行的人们面朝不同的方向，他们仍处于同一片星空下。</p></div><div style="display: block;               瓦尔特
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Welt</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/4ef5ca2ce2cde8d59f1bd70eab7522bb_716739230393413373.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">彭博</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll hasVBar" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden scroll; margin-right: -15px;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">老成持重的前逆熵盟主，继承了「世界」之名，曾屡次拯救世界于灭亡的边缘。</p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap; min-height: 1em;"></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">灾难结束后，瓦尔特一度卸下命运交付的重担，成为一名动画分镜师。然而圣方丹事件结束后，瓦尔特被迫与事件始作俑者去向星门另一侧。</p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap; min-height: 1em;"></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">或许连他自己也未曾料到，在那里等待着的，将是全新的旅途和同伴。</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; z-index: -1000; pointer-events: none;"><object type="text/html" tabindex="-1" data="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/saved_resource(9).html" style="display: block;               丹恒
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Dan Heng</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/f81c0125929fe168ac2175fc7281a902_7413180509340604345.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">李春胤</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%; min-height: 1em;"></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">丹恒对自己的过往始终讳莫如深，他与列车同行正是为了摆脱自己曾亲手造就的一切。</p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap; min-height: 1em;"></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">然而，列车真的会带着他远离「过去」么？</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; z-index: -1000; pointer-events: none;"><object type="text/html" tabindex="-1" data="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/saved_resource(10).html" style="display: block;               三月七
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">March 7th</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/efe0cd9e61117776212f07f0a783bbb7_2580301598486259898.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">诺亚</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">精灵古怪的少女，自认热衷于这个年纪的女孩子「应当热衷」的所有事，比如照相。<br><br>从一块漂流的恒冰中苏醒，却发现自己对身世与过往都一无所知。短暂的消沉之后，她决定以重获新生的日期为自己命名。<br><br>这一天，三月七「诞生」了。</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; z-index: -1000; pointer-events: none;"><object type="text/html" tabindex="-1" data="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/saved_resource(11).html" style="display: block;               阿兰
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Arlan</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/69e521ac5be0e70740c60f89ec2200ba_2448648017717258857.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">陶典</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%;               艾丝妲
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Asta</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/59e1513a7415c4145d990218c174851a_3141454889644856788.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">龟娘</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%;               克拉拉
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Clara</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/f6a04b7a0e5ae87e8c1e55ed71c6a6a5_1286273546180834615.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">紫苏九月＆王宇航</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%;               桑博
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Sampo</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/f81c0125929fe168ac2175fc7281a902_1387945199360733465.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">刘圣博</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__panel" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; height: 100%; overflow: hidden;"><div class="__view" style="position: relative; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">口若悬河的倒货商人，只要有「利」的地方，就有桑博的身影。<br><br>桑博手中绝无仅有的情报让人不得不接近他，不过成为他的「客人」并不是什么好事。<br><br>毕竟只要价钱合适，「客人」也随时可以转化为「商品」。</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; z-index: -1000; pointer-events: none;"><object type="text/html" tabindex="-1" data="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/saved_resource(19).html" style="display: block;               佩拉
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Pela</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/efe0cd9e61117776212f07f0a783bbb7_2846424958653076994.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">宴宁</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll hasVBar" style="height: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; width: -webkit-fit-content;"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="content"><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">行事周密的银鬃铁卫情报官，年纪不大但头脑出众。<br><br>无论是部队调动、物资分配还是地形状况，佩拉都能冷静地即问即答，毫无错漏。<br><br>至于佩拉的手机壳…「这与工作无关，长官。」</p></div><div style="display: block;               希露瓦
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Serval</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/69e521ac5be0e70740c60f89ec2200ba_7523485548151431034.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">穆雪婷</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll hasVBar" style="height: 100%; line-height: 1;"><br>在永冬的贝洛伯格经营着名为「永动」的机械屋，时不时停业举办摇滚露天演出。</p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1;"><br>如果有人过问机械屋怎么赚钱…「这是兴趣，亲爱的，我不缺钱。」</p></div><div style="display: block; position: absolute;               娜塔莎
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Natasha</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/f6a04b7a0e5ae87e8c1e55ed71c6a6a5_286480906921138906.png" class="porte-wrap"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-wrap"><img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="cv-ico"> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cv-name">秦紫翼</div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="data:image/png;base64," class="voice-ico"></div> <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="story-wrap"><div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="__vuescroll" style="height: 100%;               虎克
              <div data-v-b64f4e70="" class="cover">Hook</div></div> <img data-v-b64f4e70="" src="./《崩坏：星穹铁道》官方网站——愿此行，终抵群星_files/59e1513a7415c4145d990218c174851a_3316328162124465240.png"
